Two Old Kingswoodians have been awarded the [[Victoria Cross]]
*[[William Job Maillard]] Staff Surgeon, [[Royal Navy]]
*[[Hardy Falconer Parsons]] (1897<U+2013>1917) Second Lieutenant, The Gloucestershire Regiment <ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ormerod.uk.net/Graves/CWGC/France/Somme/Villers-Faucon/villers-faucon.htm | title=Villers-Faucon Communal Cemetery| publisher=ormerod | accessdate=22 December 2010}}</ref>

